&lt;a href="https://leetcode.com/problems/top-k-frequent-words/" title="Top K Frequent Words" rel="noopener external nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank" class=" exturl"&gt;
 Top K Frequent Words
 
 &lt;i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
 
&lt;/a&gt; need to use STL priority_queue to solve the problem.&lt;/p&gt;
